# Atlas Mainframe Sentinel - Docker Stack Ignore
# No secrets, no data, just structure.

# Ignore all environment files (secrets)
**/.env
**/*.env
**/secrets/
**/credentials/

# Ignore data volumes (assuming common patterns)
**/data/
**/db/
**/config/
**/backups/
**/logs/
**/storage/

# System files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Keep structure but ignore dynamic content
!**/docker-compose.yml
!**/docker-compose.yaml
!**/*.conf.template
!**/README.md
!**/*.sh
